{{version023}}
{{flavour|Creates a large cloud of foul pestilence, slowing and rotting any living creatures it touches.}}

'''Miasma Breath''' is a monster-only spell which creates a large [[cloud]] of [[miasma]]. This [[slow]]s, [[poison]]s, and [[rot]]s the target all at once. Poison resistance and [[Formicid|stasis]] can negate the poison and slow portions of this, respectively, while rot resistance negates all effects.

{{monsters with spell}}
*{{monsterlink|Master Blaster}} (3d20 damage)

[[Category:Monster spells]]
